foreignData.name: Erntefestival
foreignData.text: Durchsuche deine Bibliothek nach bis zu X Standardland-Karten, wobei X gleich der Anzahl an unterschiedlichen Stärken unter den Kreaturen ist, die du kontrollierst. Bringe die Karten getappt ins Spiel und mische danach.

foreignData.name: Celebrar la cosecha
foreignData.text: Busca en tu biblioteca hasta X cartas de tierra básica, donde X es la cantidad de fuerzas distintas entre las criaturas que controlas. Pon esas cartas en el campo de batalla giradas y luego baraja.

foreignData.name: Célébrer les moissons
foreignData.text: Cherchez dans votre bibliothèque jusqu'à X cartes de terrain de base, X étant le nombre de forces différentes parmi les créatures que vous contrôlez. Mettez ces cartes sur le champ de bataille, engagées, puis mélangez.

foreignData.name: Celebrare il Raccolto
foreignData.text: Passa in rassegna il tuo grimorio per trovare fino a X carte terra base, dove X è il numero di valori di forza diversi tra le creature che controlli. Metti quelle carte sul campo di battaglia TAPpate, poi rimescola.

foreignData.name: 収穫の宴
foreignData.text: あなたのライブラリーから基本土地・カード最大Ｘ枚を探し、タップ状態で戦場に出す。その後、ライブラリーを切り直す。Ｘはあなたがコントロールしているクリーチャーの中のパワーの種類数に等しい。

name: Celebrate the Harvest
originalText: Search your library for up to X basic land cards, where X is the number of different powers among creatures you control. Put those cards onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.

rulings.text: Celebrate the Harvest looks at the creatures you control as it resolves to determine how many basic lands cards you can search for. For example, if you control a 1/1 creature and a 2/1 creature at that time, there are two different powers among creatures you control.

text: Search your library for up to X basic land cards, where X is the number of different powers among creatures you control. Put those cards onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
